OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,FThe mother of an autistic teenager
OL,7,Fsays she was "embarrassed" after
OL,8,Fpolice came to her house when she took
OL,9,Fhim out of school amid a row over
OL,10,Fclassroom support.
OL,12,FBecky Irvin's 15-year-old son Jacob
OL,13,Fwas given an autism diagnosis last
OL,14,Fyear - six years after teachers first
OL,15,Fsuggested he may have the
OL,16,Fdevelopmental disability.
