OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,FDespite his diagnosis, he is still
OL,7,Fawaiting an Education Health and Care
OL,8,FPlan (EHCP), which would outline his
OL,9,Fneeds and could unlock funding for
OL,10,Fextra support in school.
OL,12,FJacob attends Archbishop Sentamu
OL,13,FAcademy, a mainstream school in east
OL,14,FHull, but his mother keeps him at home
OL,15,Fif he is struggling with anxiety.
OL,17,FIn the last 12 months, she has been
OL,18,Ffined multiple times over school
OL,19,Fabsences. In April police knocked on
OL,20,Ftheir door while they were away.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
