OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,F"They knocked on the neighbours' door
OL,7,Fas well and I was so embarrassed,"
OL,8,FBecky said.
OL,10,F"The next door neighbour said they'd
OL,11,Fasked if they'd seen Jacob because he
OL,12,Fhadn't been in school.
OL,14,F"The kids didn't want to come home.
OL,15,FJacob was nonverbal all the way home
OL,16,Fand shut himself in his bedroom and
OL,17,Fdidn't come out for three days.
