OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,F"I rang the solicitors after that
OL,7,Fbecause I (had more) contact from the
OL,8,Fschool in that one week than I've been
OL,9,Fasking for for a year."
OL,11,FShe said the police visit came after
OL,12,Fshe took Jacob out of school following
OL,13,Fa meeting with school leaders in which
OL,14,Fher repeated requests for better in-
OL,15,Fclass support were denied.
