OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,F"I feel awful," she continued. "I know
OL,7,Fthe school has a lack of staff and
OL,8,Ftraining but going through this on a
OL,9,Fdaily basis, they need to understand
OL,10,Fhow awful this is."It's detrimental to
OL,11,Feverybody in the family's health - not
OL,12,Fjust Jacob's. It's soul destroying to
OL,13,Fsee him like that. It hurts so much."
OL,15,FMore than one in 100 people are on the
OL,16,Fautism spectrum and there are around
OL,17,F700,000 autistic adults and children
OL,18,Fin the UK. It can affect how they
OL,19,Fcommunicate and interact with the
OL,20,Fworld around them.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
