OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,FDepending on their individual
OL,7,Fdiagnosis and EHCP, some autistic
OL,8,Fchildren are given one-to-one support
OL,9,Fin class or are helped in different
OL,10,Fways with issues like communication or
OL,11,Fanxiety.
OL,13,FBecky's frustrations over assessment
OL,14,Fdelays and support are shared by many
OL,15,Ffamilies in Hull and further afield.
OL,17,FFigures obtained by ITV News under the
OL,18,FFreedom of Information Act show that,
OL,19,Fas of June this year, there were 202
OL,20,Fchildren in Hull waiting to find out
OL,21,Fif they had be given EHCP.
