OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,FThey were among almost 2,900 due to be
OL,7,Fassessed for extra support across
OL,8,FYorkshire and Lincolnshire, while 376
OL,9,Fwere waiting for a place in a special
OL,10,Fschool.
OL,12,FNicola Robinson, the co-founder of the
OL,13,FAim Higher parent support charity,
OL,14,Fhelps around 600 families of children
OL,15,Fwith special educational needs in Hull
OL,16,Fand East Yorkshire including Jacob's.
