OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,FShe says her charity had calls from
OL,7,Fseven families, who were taking their
OL,8,Fchildren out of school altogether, in
OL,9,Fthe space of two weeks this summer
OL,10,Fbecause of their frustrations over a
OL,11,Flack of additional help or specialist
OL,12,Fschool places.
OL,14,FNicola said: "Parents don't want to
OL,15,Fkeep their children out of school. It
OL,16,Fcan be a safe place for children and
OL,17,Frespite for parents - it's really
OL,18,Fimportant that we're getting that in
OL,19,Fthere as well.
OL,26,@vD@NOU
