OL,3,CPolice sent to home of autistic boy in
OL,4,Crow over school absences
OL,6,F"We need to not be fining (families
OL,7,Fover absences) but understanding and
OL,8,Fworking with families to find out why
OL,9,Fthey can't get into school. What can
OL,10,Fwe do to make that better?"
OL,12,FHull City Council would not comment on
OL,13,Findividual cases but said the Hope
OL,14,FSentamu Learning Trust, which runs
OL,15,FJacob's school, was committed to
OL,16,Fworking in partnership with the
OL,17,Fcouncil to "improve the educational
OL,18,Foutcomes for all the children,
OL,19,Fincluding those with special
OL,20,Feducational needs" despite challenges
OL,21,Fin "the national landscape for SEND".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
