OL,6,FA spokesperson added that the council
OL,7,Fis taking "effective action" and has
OL,8,Freduced EHCP assessment waiting times
OL,9,Ffrom nine months to 15 weeks, while
OL,10,Fdelivering free-to-all SEND training
OL,11,Fto schools.
OL,13,FThey said: "Special educational needs
OL,14,Fare being identified and supported
OL,15,Fearlier, so that they do not escalate
OL,16,Fto the point where an EHCP is required.
